Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:07.35,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（危险）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:08.10,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（不要犯困）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.45,0:00:09.45,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（不—要—犯—困）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.51,0:00:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.62,0:00:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀—！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.21,0:00:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.84,0:02:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.14,0:02:11.89,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,…事件发生的时间是昨天下午三点多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经早上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做了个奇怪的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是那种梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,租金3万日圆以内  距离车站步行1分钟…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,电视一直开着的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚会下雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经这个时候了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  我到底在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要到什么时候才能变成蝴蝶呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,睡懒觉也得有个分寸哟  青虫君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「7月14日  冰凉和郁馥」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说来…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天小宫没来叫我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不会是小宫也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快起来  小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,考试迟到就不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然小宫也学习到很晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,学习？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是单纯的睡过了头而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都睡了十二个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,十二个小时…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来总算能赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时候就会觉得住在学校门前真是好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻学姐  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.10,0:03:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个？香草
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竖琴？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.33,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：由乃把herb误听作harp了）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了  寻学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开始学竖琴了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不贵么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是最后一天考试了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我带齐文具了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才急急忙忙的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个不是橡皮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可塑橡皮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫  你带了两块橡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个这么着…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这一个得这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里要如此做…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶…偶然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个这么着…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个选这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后下一个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得一定是弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家开始动笔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野屋老师的美术课考试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,问一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这照片上的人物是谁呢？
