Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么美术考试会有日本史的题目…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:15.45,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}问二\N这照片上的人物是谁呢？\N请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,织田信长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:19.95,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}问三\N这照片上的人物是谁呢？\N请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本…本名叫什么来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,摩艾？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请举出你喜欢的一位艺术家的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就不是考试而是调查问卷了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请举出一幅你喜欢的绘画作品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.85,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}问十二\N请举出一幅你喜欢的绘画作品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绘画…绘画…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请举出一件你喜欢的雕塑作品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雕塑…雕塑…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,列举三个以上  你最喜欢的吉野屋老师的动人之处告诉校长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,分值…五十分？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,滥用职权
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:28.17,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（我肚子饿了）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想在试卷上涂鸦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很明显和在写字时不一样的声音不绝于耳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:42.27,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（手痒痒）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手痒痒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手痒痒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手痒痒！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:07:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样期末考试就全部结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一排的同学请把试卷收上来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,分数最低的同学的答题卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要张贴到校门口去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以做好心理准备哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由于被校长狠狠地训了一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不张贴了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫  怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想到考试结束了就是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就太过兴奋而不能集中精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过说起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,湛蓝的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:07:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,耀眼的太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天了夏天了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,GO  GO  黑色素
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  日光浴哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是来晒太阳的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一起晒黑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫  在么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来了～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫莫非你刚在房顶上？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能做那么危险的事情哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,摔下来就不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做日光浴么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然夏天就得是健康的黑色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫真是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,腹部都弄脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:08:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,腹部好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.43,0:09:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还真是热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.89,0:09:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说因为在夏天这是理所应当的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过就这样也很可以享受一番呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有什么变凉快的方法呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼故事  鬼故事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,台阶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:21.93,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnzhunyuan\b1}（注：「怪談」、「階段」两个词发音一样）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说爬到最上面会很凉快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是中途就会举手投降了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是鬼故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  台阶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是鬼故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了是台阶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是鬼故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是台阶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好热～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是外星人～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,地底人～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:10:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无农药栽培的胡萝卜～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的  沙英学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也经常这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们做…做…做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也…也不敲门就闯入别人屋里来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是个大太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们想或许一楼比二楼凉快…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  考试也全考完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沙英学姐也和我们一块儿玩的话会很开心…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊  寻似乎很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还说要在屋里制作作品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天也没有什么特别的要做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  宫子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么？翻翻看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有什么有意思的东西呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「我最喜欢和美了」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,俊君突然站了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对着逐渐沉下水平线的太阳大喊着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已超过预定时间五个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:20.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在淅沥的雨中连伞也没撑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,优作只是一个劲地在等着恭子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么优作是那么的温柔呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  沙英学姐真是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不是更热了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去泳池么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,泳池么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.93,0:11:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你邀别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么？为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:12:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…那说来很难为情…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是个锯子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.33,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（由乃想说的是这个…金づち(旱鸭子)）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说错得很离谱…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我明白那玩意同样会在水里沉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英学姐稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿泳池来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拿泳池来？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,橡胶泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…也罢  虽说我就想会是那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你有这玩意？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,决定一个人住的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父母让我带上这个的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很不错的父母吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个在一个人住的时候有必要么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说即使租没有浴室的房间也没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么父母啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过   这个泳池的话由乃也no problem了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:58.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  或许用这个我也行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么没有问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这泳池里你想溺水也没法子吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说来宫子  你有泳衣么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有学校发的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那样不就觉得像是在学校游泳一样么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一件去年买的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确实在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宫子  这个你拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,T-shirt和比基尼短裤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？沙英学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么比基尼没有上下配套呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是弄丢了上装什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是不想被宫子说么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么「胸部好紧啊」之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙…沙英学姐很苗条呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或…或许是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对哟  沙英学姐这里有个院子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是住一楼的人的特权
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  由乃来吹气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知…知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:32.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傍晚前能吹起来么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弄错了弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非由乃没用过气泵？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  过去也玩过橡胶泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那时候我还小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是爸爸帮我弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过说来这玩意平时不大用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用的时候就是让橡胶泳池啊橡胶艇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种的气垫膨胀起来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,泳圈啊沙滩排球啊什么的用嘴吹还方便些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别看我这样  气泵可是我的绝活哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都差不多想在简历里的特长一栏写上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.56,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（使用气泵三级）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃  去换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宫子  泳池就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,气泵把…空气…送进去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,送空气…很费劲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我…很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.75,0:15:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在做什么啊  寻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自我忍耐比赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:16:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是在进行制作么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…我在制作能穿着夏天的短装的苗条身材
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这种制作么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不说这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英你们这样子是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在戏水的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫拿来了橡胶泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为太开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本想也邀寻学姐一起来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:16:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然说到夏天就应该是火锅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我可没有听说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:05.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说来  这么热你还吃得下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  偶尔也会想吃火锅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以摄取许多蔬菜  对健康有好处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢什么火锅？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢咸杂烩火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是日式牛肉火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是什锦火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.23,0:17:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是泡菜火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为能减肥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  火锅就得大家一起吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  别在那儿光吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  火锅奉行出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:36.48,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（火锅奉行：吃火锅时乐于规定他人食材何时放入，何时能吃的人）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么火锅会有奉行呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发号施令这种了不起的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,除了奉行也还有很多其他的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会说是火锅社长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说了别光吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火锅社长是火锅职员的社长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火锅同心什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.32,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：江户时代类似警察一类的下级官差）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火锅老中什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:00.61,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：江户幕府时期最高的官职）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火锅总统什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火锅总理大臣什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我～说～了～别光吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.51,0:18:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火锅预告师什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火锅领头美容师什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火锅Best Genius什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好热～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到底在做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想想今天真的好热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像平常一般的运动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是更加健康的减肥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冰凉冰凉的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:55.15,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,现在插播特别新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:56.75,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天以来一直持续着的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样只看着天空的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会感觉像在海里悠闲地漂着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  会哦会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是白令海了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是白令海？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加勒比海什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爱琴海什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,更加休闲的大海也是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大海吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有一阵子没去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起大海我还是喜欢泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为脚不能着地是很可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是锯子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,锯子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  锯啊锯啊锯啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过为什么海边的店里的的拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会有特别好的味道呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咖喱饭也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  食物已经说够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说完全跑题了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天做了个奇怪的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直被斗篷一样的红色的布团追着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个奇怪的梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梦是表现人的深层心理的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说由乃不想被红色的斗篷追着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你照搬吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.72,0:20:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说或许那玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.87,0:20:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是卷积云？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每年看着那云都会想的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫  暑假你准备怎么过？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是去大海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊  我可是锯子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就说那个锯子是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,锯子  锯子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接近傍晚的晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:55.90,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（夏天的海）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么样对付过了考试
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至少也没有像是要开红灯的科目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那个莫非是红色的窗帘？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红色的窗帘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,略作「红灯」？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:11.67,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：文字游戏）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冷笑话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.22,0:21:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,青虫君它…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,青虫君它…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蛾…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.67,0:21:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,青虫君原来是蛾？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有点奇形怪状呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.53,0:21:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:21:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:22:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要上这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.30,0:22:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  从窗子飞走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.74,0:22:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.65,0:22:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到寻学姐屋里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,7月14日  完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.82,0:23:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.41,0:23:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小时侯做过晴天娃娃么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  做过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.45,0:23:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,郊游什么的运动会什么的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.16,0:23:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为  面对自然现象做这种事情也是白搭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.26,0:23:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比平时起得更早  背上背包
